translate ru LifeInRahayal2_41402a02:
    # "Early the next day, Sarah had finished her breakfast and quickly took out to the streets of the city."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_b6c50033:
    # "She had some money, and now a place to stay, but she knew she didn't really have all that much."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_1f6e8f96:
    # "Her money would see her through for maybe a month at best."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_d67ded71:
    # "Enough to give her space to breathe, too little to simply sit and be idle."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_f08205e2:
    # "She had to make the most of her time here, and Sarah was eager not to waste a moment of it."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_6046e25e:
    # "Though she had set out with a clear goal, it wasn't long before Sarah found herself starting to become distracted."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_89227cc3:
    # "She had lived most of her life in the capital of Rosanna, which to her had appeared a large city."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_0d10267f:
    # "Then she had arrived in Lethram, which had appeared to her larger still."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ca8e9405:
    # "But as she walked over one of the great plaza's of the city of Rahayal, Sarah could not help but be in awe."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_03d27e88:
    # "The city of Rahayal was like a vast mountain, which by virtue of perspective rendered all other things small."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ead96966:
    # "Never in her life could she have imagined a city of this size could exist."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_68f28796:
    # "Everywhere she looked, swarms of people moved about in endless productivity."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_28a476ec:
    # "Off in the far distance, the city stretched on as far as she could see."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_504e0984:
    # "Massive monuments that would have put the castle of her youth to shame, towered up and cast long shadows."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_89795976:
    # "When Sarah tried to hold the whole of the city in her mind, it made her dizzy."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_75619c7d:
    # "But above all, there was one object that always loomed larger than any other, and could be seen from virtually every direction."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_25bc4005:
    # "The Black Pyramid, home of the Eternal Court, where the rulers of the Empire gathered and laid their plans upon the world."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_4a32c97a:
    # "Though it seemed near to her, Sarah quickly realized it was an optical illusion."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_a86435c3:
    # "The thing was simply so enormous that it always appeared close."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_f163738b:
    # "As much as it drew her own attention, it seemed to leave everyone else entirely unbothered, hardly worth a glance."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_9b1c896c:
    # "And as the day went on, Sarah realized she too was quickly becoming oblivious to the thing."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ecc0e66e:
    # "Less and less she found herself looking at it, until before long, she hardly considered the construct worth even a brief glance."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_6ef1d8b8:
    # "Still exploring the city, Sarah made her way through streets and crowds, taking in all the sights."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_21172aaa:
    # "Though much of the city filled with awe, there was one element that forever troubled her."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_4b99ae20:
    # "Slavery, banned in the Union Kingdoms for her home, was very much alive in Rahayal and the rest of the Mythran Empire."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_69294bd6:
    # "In fact, by most accounts, the majority of the inhabitants of both the city and the empire, were slaves."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_47e3b1c3:
    # "Sarah watched them, bound with metal, marked with symbols that she could not understand."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_cbdc5a1e:
    # "At first, she saw the worst of them."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_d0597f59:
    # "The young men and women, dragged about nearly naked in long chain gangs, going from one place to another."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ec3d2ec4:
    # "But soon, the more she paid attention, Sarah realized that the slavery ran deeper."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_f63bb324:
    # "The man or woman that pulled the slaves along by chain, often also bore the markings of a slave."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_88c18c12:
    # "Soldiers. Merchants. Officials."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_3f1744ee:
    # "The slaves of this Empire came in every kind, both lowly and high."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_6feab766:
    # "Sarah was watching a young woman following in the footsteps of what appeared to be her master."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_92ee270d:
    # "Her head turned low, she looked at Sarah for a brief moment, and their eyes met."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_4b4ecad9:
    # "The moment passed as quickly as it occurred, yet Sarah was left startled by it."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_4d4ca1eb:
    # "The girl had looked so much like herself, yet in her eyes, a hollowness."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_54f1d228:
    # "Everything in her life had taught her to be good. She knew that she had to save the girl."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_880bc22f:
    # "And yet, she equally knew that in this place, she was powerless."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_52fc27c7:
    # "Not only could she do nothing to save the girl physically, the truth was that the law also sided with the slavers."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_e5347003:
    # "If Sarah did anything, at best, the guards would drag her away."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_af0452aa:
    # "And so instead, Sarah stood only nailed to the ground, watching something evil unfold."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_778b4af6:
    # "The girl dissapeared along with her master, turning down some street."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_c5a61e34:
    # "A voice broke snapped Sarah from her stunned condition."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_32057862:
    # "Official" "Work! Work!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_f501577a:
    # "Sarah turned to look at the man shouting."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_1526e469:
    # "She saw a man, well dressed and seemingly full of confidence, shouting at the corner of a street."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_fd132cf4:
    # "A small crowd of people was gathering."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_e71c88ba:
    # "Sarah walked towards them."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_34903bf3:
    # "Official" "We're looking for workers, you got a pair of hands that work, we got work!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_43e44657:
    # "Sarah pressed through the crowd to get closer to the man."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_40f95494:
    # "Slave" "I can work!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_3d491137:
    # "She heard a man, bound in iron, call out."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ef78e616:
    # "The official shook his head."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_bd7fd7e6:
    # "Official" "No slaves, not for this job. Freemen and Freewomen only."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_b95298bd:
    # "Woman" "What's the work?"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_eb1bf6c1:
    # "More voices called out, asking questions."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_1aa41557:
    # "Official" "One at a time, please!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_3798f468:
    # "The crowd seemed to quiet down a bit."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_bda5bd57:
    # "Official" "I'm looking for people able to do servant work. House cleaning, cooking, basic skills."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_c5bd2d26:
    # "Sarah thought about it."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ff743d4a:
    # "The truth was that her noble birth had shielded her from such hard work."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_e515a126:
    # "Then again, she did imagine she'd able to learn it quickly enough."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_98ed7d36:
    # "Man" "What's the catch?"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_e324d08a:
    # "The official seemed to suddenly become nervous."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_5c4aea95:
    # "Official" "No catch at all. Fair work for fair pay!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_6b4cbe95:
    # "Woman" "Where?"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_90019011:
    # "Official" "Where? What does that matter! A servant in one house is a servant in another, no?!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_2423f721:
    # "Official" "It shouldn't matter where!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_127f73f3:
    # "The crowd become more unruly, sensing that something was up."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_dfaca51c:
    # "Before long, more were yelling, asking him where the work was."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_a2773524:
    # "The official threw up hands hands."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_9b939996:
    # "Official" "Fine!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_92831ee3:
    # "Official" "The positions open are for servants at the Estate of the honourable Gilead."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_7cfccf50:
    # "Hearing the last word, the crowd seemed to explode in yelling and cursing."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_684fbc29:
    # "Instantly, Sarah saw that large numbers of people began to walk away."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ff524d38:
    # "Those few that remained were mostly there to hurl a last few insults at the official, before they also left."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_1d64a467:
    # "Sarah turned to one of the women that was walking away."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_416f71ef:
    # s "Why are you leaving?"
    s ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_78964f01:
    # "Woman" "Cause you'd be mad to be workin at that freak's Estate."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_3dd24a5c:
    # s "Mad? Why?"
    s ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_13a6f83f:
    # "Woman" "Trust me, somethin twisted goes up on there."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_b8432d48:
    # "Woman" "Servants go missin and each week the tryin to sucker new fools workin there."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_a7e0940b:
    # "Woman" "You value your life, don't go there."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_b99993d2:
    # "The woman pulled away from Sarah and stormed off."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ae263f5b:
    # "Sarah turned back to look at the official."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_ce8c7e75:
    # "The large crowd had dwindled down to five people."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_aa8b96b2:
    # "Two men, two women and herself."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_7c6ae088:
    # "The official sighed."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_6f30127b:
    # "Official" "Well, forget about them. And don't believe the rumors they peddle either!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_1f9b3a29:
    # "Man" "Rumors?"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_96a55f7a:
    # "The official smiled."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_1bfe391f:
    # "Official" "Nothing. Forget I said anything."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_83c41ab0:
    # "Official" "Instead, how about that job? If you can do a hard day's work, it's all yours! And the pay is very fair!"
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_65336f03:
    # "One by one, the men and the women stepped forward and began signing the working contracts."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_a47d73c3:
    # "When the last of them had signed, the official suddenly pointed directly at Sarah."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_f4613d93:
    # "Official" "You there, girly."
    ""

translate ru LifeInRahayal2_aeff54a0:
    # "Official" "How about it? We got kitchen work as well, I promise it will pay well!"
    ""

